&lt;li&gt;Zhongnan Xu and John R. Kitchin, Probing the Coverage Dependence of Site and AdsorbateConfigurational Correlations on (111) Surfaces of LateTransition Metals, J. Phys. Chem. C, 2014.&lt;/li&gt;
